  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Effect of Lorcaserin Hydrochloride on Smoking Cessation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 12-Week, Multicenter, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled Parallel-group Phase 2 Dose Selection Study of Lorcaserin Hydrochloride, an Oral 5-HT2C Receptor Agonist for Smoking Cessation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
