  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In smokers who are motivated to stop smoking, treatment with lorcaserin compared with placebo
      will provide greater abstinence as measured by the last 4 weeks of treatment (Weeks 9-12)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
